---
title: Smokey Chicken & Veggie Traybake with Garlic Mash & Corn Cobs
description: Create a family feast of colourful veggies and succulent chicken. Paprika brings a moreish smokey flavour to the chicken and veggies, while the garlic mash is perfect for soaking up all the juices. This is a meal you'll want again and again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ddf0525840bd34a9375fb70-9fe2c6c2.jpg
